Package: TerraclimateR
Type: Package
Title: Download Terraclimate Data in Tidy Format
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Julian Selke
Maintainer: Julian Selke <juli4n.selke@gmail.com>
Description: The terraclimate data set by Abatzoglou et al. (2018) provides data on 14 climatic variables through time since 1958 at 4km resolution in space and monthly resolution in time. TerraclimateR implements a single function (`get_terraclim`) to access these data and import them directly into R in long format.    
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
